item.dc:creator: hackyyt
item.content:encoded:
COVID Made Easy.

Track your symptoms post-COVID Diagnosis. Get emergency services and helplines at your fingertips.

The perfect platform for a seamless experience for the self-quarantined.

Get Started

HIghlights

Welcome to Your COVID Tracker

Track your day-to-day symptoms.

  • Body temperature
  • Blood pressure
  • Body pain
  • Breathlessness
  • Coughing
  • Oximeter readings
  • Sense of taste/smell

Get personalized suggestions and help based on the seriousness of your symptoms. You can also keep a track of your mental health during such an intense period.

One click away from medical help,

during emergencies.

Know your Tracker

The tracker is tailor made for navigating your COVID Diagnosis. And regular updates keep up with the variations in the symptoms. Be sure to check it out!

View Symptom Tracker

Symptom Analysis

Very Critical

Emergency Button
Receive immediate help--from calling an ambulance to oxygen supply--we've got you covered.

Critical

Helplines
Connects you to the nearest available medical facility or helplines for mental health.

Moderate-Low

Suggestions/Tips
Get personalized tips, helpful suggestions and reminders according to your symptoms, to keep yourself in check.

Sign Up.

In case of queries, call us (+91) 6448725780 or use the form below to sign up.

Click here after you've signed up.

GEt In Touch

Come on the other side of the page. Tell us, we're listening.
